title: Jeff Sessions fires McCabe, Beyonce and Jay-Z Go On The Run II,  and Little Big Shots returns for Season 3
itunes:title: Jeff Sessions fires McCabe, Beyonce and Jay-Z Go On The Run II,  and Little Big Shots returns for Season 3
description:
The crew goes over the firing of former Deputy Director McCabe. They also talk about Beyonce and Jay-Z Tour and the Beyonce songs that men should never sing. Little Big Shots makes its return to TV and Catch Fool #1 and his Prank Call Go Big or Go Home. Enjoy!
